Ask HN: What is your reason for not choosing to use PHP for your next project?
text:
I've been reading about different programming languages and, while I have limited exposure, it feels like PHP is one of the most mature languages designed specifically for creating websites. That being said, I rarely see it being talked about.

So what is your reason for not using PHP?

Ask HN: Best self-powered security system?
text:
I am looking for a security system (camera, etc) to be installed in a remote location, served by solar power + battery.

Surprisingly, I didn't find anything at a reasonable price that can also offer several days of autonomy.

Anyone can offer suggestions?
